name: Universe #184
description: Universe #184 - Black ice covered all of Pestot for all eternity. It was so dark that it went through the void unnoticed by any others. A miracle happened when a piece of black ice slowly turned blue, getting warmer compared to the rest. It didn't go unnoticed as 184 was close to it. It held the universe as it slowly started it's journey in getting warmer. It's help was definitely welcome as their embrace became stronger.
